ux.name: ux

revisions.description: This MIB will describe the entries for the SBC line of products.

ux.description: The MIB module for net.com entities.

uxPortTable.name: uxPortTable
uxPortTable.description: The list of ports in the system. In general this table applies to T1/E1 ports and SIP SG except as noted on individual attributes.

uxPortEntry.name: uxPortEntry
uxPortEntry.description: An entry containing information about the ports in the system.

uxPTIndex.name: uxPTIndex
uxPTIndex.description: Index for the port table. This number is assigned sequentially.

uxPTShelf.name: uxPTShelf
uxPTShelf.description: The shelf number this port is assigned to.

uxPTSlot.name: uxPTSlot
uxPTSlot.description: The slot this port is assigned to. A slot number of 0 indicates the row is associated with a SIP SG.

uxPTPort.name: uxPTPort
uxPTPort.description: The port number (within the slot). For SIP SG this value would represent the row number of the SG.

uxPTCurrentCalls.name: uxPTCurrentCalls
uxPTCurrentCalls.description: The current number of calls active on this port. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxPTTotalCalls.name: uxPTTotalCalls
uxPTTotalCalls.description: The total number of calls received on this port. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxPTConnectedCalls.name: uxPTConnectedCalls
uxPTConnectedCalls.description: The number of calls answered on this port. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxPTRefusedCalls.name: uxPTRefusedCalls
uxPTRefusedCalls.description: The number of calls refused on this port. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxPTErroredCalls.name: uxPTErroredCalls
uxPTErroredCalls.description: The number of errors on this port. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxPTEgressCallAttempts.name: uxPTEgressCallAttempts
uxPTEgressCallAttempts.description: The total number of Egress call attempts on this port.

uxPTEgressCallsAccepted.name: uxPTEgressCallsAccepted
uxPTEgressCallsAccepted.description: The number of Egress successfull call attempts on this port. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxPTEgressCallsCompleted.name: uxPTEgressCallsCompleted
uxPTEgressCallsCompleted.description: The number of successfully completed Egress calls on this port.

uxPTEgressCallsRejected.name: uxPTEgressCallsRejected
uxPTEgressCallsRejected.description: The number of Egress calls from this port that were rejected. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxPTIngressCallAttempts.name: uxPTIngressCallAttempts
uxPTIngressCallAttempts.description: The total number of Ingress call attempts on this port.

uxPTIngressCallsAccepted.name: uxPTIngressCallsAccepted
uxPTIngressCallsAccepted.description: The total number of Ingress calls accepted on this port. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxPTIngressCallsCompleted.name: uxPTIngressCallsCompleted
uxPTIngressCallsCompleted.description: The number of successfully completed Ingress calls on this port.

uxPTIngressCallsRejected.name: uxPTIngressCallsRejected
uxPTIngressCallsRejected.description: The number of Ingress calls to this port that were rejected. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxPTBlockedCalls.name: uxPTBlockedCalls
uxPTBlockedCalls.description: The number of calls blocked per channel per port. Only applicable to ISDN ports.

uxPTEgressBlockedCalls.name: uxPTEgressBlockedCalls
uxPTEgressBlockedCalls.description: The number of Egress calls blocked on this port. Only applicable to ISDN ports.

uxPTIngressBlockedCalls.name: uxPTIngressBlockedCalls
uxPTIngressBlockedCalls.description: The number of Ingress calls blocked on this port. Only applicable to ISDN ports.

uxPTEgressCurrentCalls.name: uxPTEgressCurrentCalls
uxPTEgressCurrentCalls.description: The number of Egress active calls on this port. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxPTIngressCurrentCalls.name: uxPTIngressCurrentCalls
uxPTIngressCurrentCalls.description: The number of Ingress active calls on this port. Not applicable to CAS ports.

uxChannelStatusTable.name: uxChannelStatusTable

uxSGStatsIntervalTable.name: uxSGStatsIntervalTable
